mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: SQUARE DANCES "Marianne", "Changeable U", and "Texarkana Star". ROUND DANCES "Tennessee Two-Step", and "Jack & Jill Two-Step - R/M". SPECIAL FEATURES "Convention Highlights", "A Float In Flowers", "East Africa Dances", "England's Farewell to Cal", "Two For California", "Progress On the Island", "M.S.U. Features Square Dancing", "They Dance Down Under Too", and "Square Dancing - A Social Welfare Medium".
